<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說喔，<delay20 />我在昨天的平安夜裡，<delay20 />
收到了<delay8 />向聖誕老人祈求的禮物喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我本來還很擔心我的願望<delay8 />
會不會沒傳達給聖誕老人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來願望有好好傳達到呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">因為收到聖誕老人的禮物太過高興，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />導致我昨晚難以入睡啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />那個我一直想要的禮物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想起打開包裝紙的那瞬間，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就會不禁露出笑容呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你<delay8 />昨天和我交換禮物～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興能收到你送的禮物喔，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年再來交換禮物吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你昨天送的禮物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興能收到那個喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明年還想跟你交換禮物，<delay20 />
所以我得趁現在開始<delay8 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好考慮
明年要送的禮物才行～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興<delay8 />昨天能同時收到聖誕老人<delay8 />
和<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />送的禮物喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然拆開禮物包裝紙時，<delay20 />
就是有種特別的樂趣，<delay20 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開心的程度
是平常的數倍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你昨天送的禮物，<delay frames="40" />
我很高興<delay8 />能收到那個喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且<delay8 />我還收到了聖誕老人的禮物，<delay20 />
今年的平安夜真是令人開心啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我今天<delay20 />就來特別教你<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是如何度過聖誕節的吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先是散步～<delay8 />再來是吃飯～<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後睡個午覺後，<delay8 />起床玩玩具<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等，這跟平時沒兩樣啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為昨天是平安夜，<delay8 />
所以我就打算待在家裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />準備<delay8 />招待聖誕老人<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惜最後還是沒能見到他～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想他一定是趁我睡著時，<delay20 />
悄悄地回去了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>